The paper discusses fall detection techniques, which are related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and computer vision (cs.CV) as they involve analyzing sensor data to detect falls. The paper also discusses machine learning methods for fall detection, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of sensors and data analysis, which are related to cybernetics (cs.CY) and signal processing (cs.SI).
